== Umugambi ==
Mubintu bisa nkubuzima butunganye, abagore batatu beza bagiye kuzuza imyaka mirongo itatu bagerageza bashize amanga kugirango bahindure ubuzima bwabo nubwo ibizazane bitabura. Hamwe nubukwe busa nkaho bugiye kurimbuka kuva mbere, kugeza kumukandida udashoboka no gukurikirana urukundo rutagira iherezo, inshuti eshatu ziziga amasomo akomeye yubuzima, imbogamizi zubukwe, impfu zo gukundana nibihembo bya guseka neza mu gihu cy'akababaro. Ishusho Yuzuye itanga ubushishozi bwamabara kandi asetsa mwisi aho ibintu byose bitunganye nkubuzima bwawe ninshuti zawe.   

